name: Comando de inicialização
func:
msg.payload = "setup.operating_mode=active
modem.protocol.isoc.physical.set(tari=tari_12_50, return_link_freq=LF80, data_1_length=d1_len_20, rt_modulation=rt_mod_pr, tr_encoding=tr_enc_fm0, interrogator_mode=dense)
antennas.1.conducted_power=250
antennas.2.conducted_power=160
antennas.3.conducted_power=160
antennas.4.conducted_power=160
tag.reporting.depart_time=1500
tag.reporting.depart_fields=tag_id antenna time user_data
tag.reporting.arrive_fields=tag_id antenna time user_data
reader.events.register(" + msg.payload + ", event.tag.arrive)
reader.events.register(" + msg.payload + ", event.tag.depart)
"
return msg;

name: Comando alterar ID Reader
func:
msg.payload = "tag.write_id(new_tag_id=" + msg.payload.id + ")\r\n"
return msg;

name: Comando checar ID Reader
func:
msg.payload = "tag.read_id()\r\n"
return msg;
